Definition.WordDefinition: Reinstall \Re`in*stall"\ (-st?l"), v. t. [Pref. re- + install: cf. F. r['e]installer.] To install again. --Milton. [1913 Webster]
reinstall v : install again; "She reinstalled the the washer after it had been repaired"
